        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>This Authorized Field Change applies to the above listed truck models built with feature code
                    04AZJ.
                </para>
                <para>It has been determined by International Truck and Engine Corporation that some of the above listed
                    truck models may have been built without the Bendix Automatic Traction Control (ATC) Module.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
